----------------------
#XMLReader
----------------------

## Introduction

> XMLReader is created to help in reading data from XML file

## Usage

> The user should send the directory path for the folder that contains one or multiple XML files and the name for the tag
 using getElementTextByTagName(String directoryPath, String tagName) method.

 >The helper will start searching for the tag in the first file to the next one until the last file in the folder,
 - if the tag found in one of these files, the data will be returned and the helper will stop searching.
 - if the tag not found in neither any file, an ElementNotFoundInXMLException will be returned.



#Requirements
> - The getElementTextByTagName method requires the following parameters:
    1-directory path: String
    2-tag name: String


